This paper discusses the construction and use of reproducing kernel Banach spaces (RKBS) in machine learning and functional analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
